  <heading>INDEX (immediates)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Create index starting from and incremented by immediate</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction populates the destination vector by setting the first element to
the first signed immediate integer operand and monotonically incrementing
the value by the second signed immediate integer operand for each subsequent element.
 This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
